      <title>特朗普命令DOJ要求法庭挑战者的货币保证金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-orders-doj-to-demand-money-bonds-from-challengers-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四宣布，一项新的政策，要求美国司法部律师在法庭上“要求”起诉政府挑战者，如果他们赢得赔偿命令阻止其行为，则应发布货币保证金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-orders-doj-to-demand-money-bonds-from-challengers-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 01:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的行政命令后，比特币沉没了市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫Crypto Czar David Sacks的X文章，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）已签署了一项行政命令，以建立战略性比特币储备金和其他数字资产的库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 00:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
